    "English": "An extremely fast <span class=\"name name-technology\">advanced processing unit</span>. Allows real-time solving of otherwise impossible calculations. However, protection against decoherence is not guaranteed.<br><br>Used in the creation of a wide range of <span class=\"name name-technology\">advanced technologies</span>.",
