  "PinObjectiveTip": {
    "English": "Craft Quantum Computer from <span class=\"name name-commodity\">Microprocessors</span>, <span class=\"name name-fuel\">Antimatter</span> and <span class=\"name name-special\">Chromatic Metal</span>.<br><br>Craft <span class=\"name name-commodity\">Microprocessors</span> or purchase at a <span class=\"name name-technology\">Trade Terminal</span>.<br>Craft <span class=\"name name-fuel\">Antimatter</span> from <span class=\"name name-special\">Chromatic Metal</span> and <span class=\"name name-fuel\">Condensed Carbon</span>.<br><span class=\"name name-special\">Chromatic Metal</span> is created in a <span class=\"name name-technology\">Refiner</span> from the <span class=\"name name-stellar\">stellar metals</span>: <span class=\"name name-commodity\">Copper</span>, <span class=\"name name-fuel\">Cadmium</span>, <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">Emeril</span> and <span class=\"name name-technology\">Indium</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "用<span class=\"name name-commodity\">微处理器</span>、<span class=\"name name-fuel\">反物质</span>和<span class=\"name name-special\">有色金属</span>制作量子电脑。<br><br>制作<span class=\"name name-commodity\">微处理器</span>或从<span class=\"name name-technology\">交易终端</span>购买。<br>用<span class=\"name name-special\">有色金属</span>和<span class=\"name name-fuel\">浓缩碳</span>制作<span class=\"name name-fuel\">反物质</span>。<br><span class=\"name name-special\">有色金属</span>可采用<span class=\"name name-technology\">精炼机</span>从<span class=\"name name-stellar\">恒星金属</span>中制得：<span class=\"name name-commodity\">铜</span>、<span class=\"name name-fuel\">镉</span>、<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">艾梅里尔</span>和<span class=\"name name-technology\">铟</span>。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "以<span class=\"name name-commodity\">微處理機</span>、<span class=\"name name-fuel\">反物質</span>和<span class=\"name name-special\">有色金屬</span>製作量子電腦。<br><br>可製作<span class=\"name name-commodity\">微處理機</span>或在<span class=\"name name-technology\">交易終端站</span>購買。<br>以<span class=\"name name-special\">有色金屬</span>和<span class=\"name name-fuel\">濃縮碳</span>製作<span class=\"name name-fuel\">反物質</span>。<br><span class=\"name name-special\">有色金屬</span>是以<span class=\"name name-technology\">精製機</span>加工以下<span class=\"name name-stellar\">星體金屬</span>而成：<span class=\"name name-commodity\">銅</span>、<span class=\"name name-fuel\">鎘</span>、<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">砪</span>、<span class=\"name name-technology\">銦</span>。"
  },
